        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Implement retry logic with exponential backoff for transient errors. Log all API responses, including error codes and timestamps, for auditing. Set up alerts for abnormal patterns, such as increased latency or failure rates, using platforms like Grafana. Regularly review API usage reports to optimize costs and performance."
